I.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "g := 6*x^3+11*x^2+6*x+1" "6#>%\"gG,**&\"\"'\"\"
\"*$%\"xG\"\"$F(F(*&\"#6F(*$F*\"\"#F(F(*&F'F(F*F(F(F(F(" }{TEXT -1 24 
